{"ts":1772778920458,"data":{"date":"2012-08-21","platform":"游戏","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/29/2c/52356_9P9Vm.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/29/2c/52356_9P9Vm.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/29/2c/52356_9P9Vm.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/29/2c/52356_9P9Vm.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/29/2c/52356_9P9Vm.jpg"},"summary":"《反恐精英：全球攻势》（CS: GO）在团队竞技游戏模式的基础上加以开发，这一模式自 12 年前发布以来一直引领至今。\r\n\r\nCS: GO 的特色是全新的地图、人物、武器以及最新版本的 CS 经典内容（de_dust 等）。此外，CS: GO 引入了全新的游戏模式、对战匹配、排行榜以及更多新的内容。\r\n\r\n“当《反恐精英》于 1999 年 8 月发售时，这个并不靠谱的模组立刻成为了世界上拥有玩家数量最多的线上 PC 动作游戏，游戏业为之一惊。”Valve 的 Doug Lombardi 如是说道。“在过去的 12 年中，它一直是世界上拥有玩家数量最多的游戏之一，引领着竞技游戏赛事，并且在全球创下了超过 2500 万套的游戏销量。CS: GO 承诺将增强屡获殊荣的 CS 系列之游戏体验，并把它带给 PC 平台、次世代主机平台和 Mac 平台的玩家。”","name":"Counter-Strike: Global Offensive","name_cn":"反恐精英：全球攻势","tags":[{"name":"FPS","count":386,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Valve","count":255,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PC","count":244,"total_cont":0},{"name":"CS:GO","count":173,"total_cont":0},{"name":"STEAM","count":163,"total_cont":0},{"name":"网游","count":91,"total_cont":0},{"name":"CS","count":75,"total_cont":0},{"name":"开箱子","count":70,"total_cont":0},{"name":"经典","count":56,"total_cont":0},{"name":"G胖的阴谋","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"射击","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2012","count":46,"total_cont":0},{"name":"单纯的竞技","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"抓好社会主义精神文明建设","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Windows","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"竞技","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Mac","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Linux","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ACT","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"第一人称射击","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Xbox360","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"hvh","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"开箱","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"普通游戏","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Online","count"